<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Renewal Reminder - Engagematic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .renewal-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .renewal-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .info-box {
            background-color: #e8f4f8;
            border-left: 4px solid #00b894;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            color: #00b894;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Subscription Renewal Reminder</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name || 'there' %>,</h2>

            <p>Your Engagematic subscription will automatically renew in <%= daysLeft || '3' %> days.</p>

            <div class="renewal-box">
                <h3>Renewal Details</h3>
                <div style="font-size: 24px; margin: 15px 0;"><%= plan || 'Pro Plan' %></div>
                <div style="font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.9;">Renewal Date: <%= renewalDate || 'In 3 days' %></div>
                <div style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 10px; opacity: 0.9;">Amount: <%= amount || '₹649' %></div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Auto-Renewal Active</h3>
                <p>Your subscription is set to automatically renew using your saved payment method. No action is required from you - we'll handle everything automatically!</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What happens on renewal?</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Your subscription continues seamlessly</li>
                <li>All your data and content remain accessible</li>
                <li>Usage limits reset for the new billing period</li>
                <li>You'll receive a confirmation email</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Need to make changes?</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Update payment method</li>
                <li>Change subscription plan</li>
                <li>Cancel auto-renewal</li>
                <li>View billing history</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= accountUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                    Manage Subscription →
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions about your subscription, reply to this email and we'll be happy to help!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for being a valued Engagematic member!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

